title: Stop Living in the Past

description:
Today I am going to give you one really incredible strategy to help you move on from the past and focus on the future that you want to create.

 

Want to master your mindset? Every Monday I send out an email with mindset tips for the week, click here to receive that email: http://mondayemail.com/
